{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason I'm trying to tell you the story, after the war, I was approached by a young friend of mine, a childhood survivor, he was a professor of psychology at UCLA, who has written many books on the Holocaust and on the second generation.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he approached me, he said to me, how could you retain your faith in God under conditions such as you went through?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Contrary to the majority of the people who gave up their faith, who became skeptic and who copped out, it was very difficult for me to find the reasons for it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a long time of deliberation, I came to the conclusion that the examples of-- it was not the norm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the exceptions that made me think of who I am and of God and the piety and the allegiance to Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them was what I told you about-- the request for execution.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other one was an incident that I want to briefly describe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a man called Reb Meyer, who came from a small town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the village anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a very, very observant man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Small in stature-- very small man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But very noticeable because he always would go around and perk up the spirit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was working on the outside in the garden detail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at the risk of his own safety, would bring food and food to the camp for the sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He would administer confession, the [NON-ENGLISH], to the people who were dying, stay with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you could find his lonely silhouette in the evening, praying some place at the end of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
